_sText: Bomb/Defusal Map made by me based on the season/prodigy inspired on the beatifull sewers in there. It has around 40-50 Spawn Points and a single bombsite. I Hope you like the map! Play it, sleep it, love it. Notes: ^This map may be come a lil boring when play it for long because of the darky textures. So after every 10 min gameplay take a rest. =) ^I will later make a GunGame version fo this map.
